Preconditions:
- The input grid must not be null.
- The input grid must have at least one row and one column.

Postconditions:
- The returned array `ans` must not be null.
- The length of the returned array `ans` must be equal to the number of columns in the input grid.
- Each element `ans[i]` in the returned array must be an integer representing the width of the `i`th column in the input grid.